<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">To Dance Without Care</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Nov 09, 2015 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Lord Jesus,
</p>

 <p>
You invite us <br></br>
to lay down our <br></br>
burdens, cares, concerns, <br></br>
fears, and anxieties, <br></br>
and give them all to you.
</p>

 <p>
Then, wrapped in the <br></br>
sweet warmth of your grace, <br></br>
we can dance in joy <br></br>
before the throne, <br></br>
as beloved children <br></br>
of the Father <br></br>
who have finally <br></br>
found their way home. <br></br></p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>



